How can I read fast while maintaining focus? Identify how new info relates with previous knowledge. Minimize mental clutter with a quick braindump. Listen to only whitenoise if anything while reading. Identify the most important word in each sentence. Look up words|concepts I don't understand. Don't re-read until after I reflect. Use mouse (cringe) to follow along. Read out loud under my breath.
